  "remarks": "Nightwolves MC is a nationalist motorcycle club founded in Moscow in 1989 and headed by Alexander Zaldastanov, with approximately 45 chapters worldwide, including chapters in many Members States of the European Union. The Nightwolves MC has been actively involved in the Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine by publicly supporting the annexation of Crimea in 2014 and the war against Ukraine in 2022, by actively spreading anti-Ukrainian and pro-Russian propaganda and by fighting with or supporting pro-Russian groups in Ukraine following the annexation of Crimea and the Russian war against Ukraine in 2022. The group is linked to “Wolf Holding Security Structures”, a company that operates training camps for “self defence” in Sevastopol, providing military training.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}